# jboss seam framework RCE CVE-2010-1871 (jboss admin console based on this framework, authentication form is vuln, Jboss 5.1 to 6.1.0 Final concerned) 
http://cvedetails.com/cve/2010-1871/
https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=615956
